    <body>
        <stanza> 
            <line>A Solemn thing within the <religion type="thing">Soul</religion> </line>
            <line>To feel itself get ripe -- </line>
            <line>And <wealth>golden</wealth> hang -- while farther up -- </line>
            <line>The Maker's Ladders stop -- </line>
            <line>And in the <nature nature_type="earth">Orchard</nature> far below -- </line>
            <line>You hear a Being -- drop -- </line>
        </stanza>
        
        <stanza>
            <line>A Wonderful -- to feel the </line>
            <line><nature nature_type="space">Sun</nature> Still toiling at the Cheek </line>
            <line>You thought was finished -- </line>
            <line>Cool of eye, and critical of Work -- </line>
            <line>He shifts the stem -- a little -- </line>
            <line>To give your Gore -- a look -- </line>
        </stanza>
        
        <stanza
            <line>But <emotion emotion_type="solemn">solemnest</emotion> -- to know </line>
            <line>Your chance in <nature nature_type="general">Harvest</nature> moves </line>
            <line>A little nearer -- Every <nature nature_type="space">Sun</nature> </line>
            <line>The Single -- to some <life>lives</life>. </line>
        </stanza>
    </body>
</poem>

